org.asoem.greyfish.utils.collect

Interface Searchable<E>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    FunctionalCollection<E>, FunctionalList<E>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FunctionalFifoBuffer, ImmutableFunctionalList

    public interface Searchable<E>
extends java.lang.Iterable<E>
    An interface for collections which want to support search operations directly, without the need to use the possibly less efficient static methods in Iterators, Iterables, Collections2 or Lists.
